	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Yes, the second value you write to $2005 controls the vertical pixel position. You might get flickering if you rely on sprite 0 and there aren't any opaque tiles to trigger it.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


